##  Usage Guide
### 1. Creating a Challenge

```clarity
(contract-call? .stacks-innovation-lab establish-innovation-challenge
    u"AI for Climate Change"
    u"Develop innovative AI solutions to combat climate change effects"
    u1000000  ;; 1 STX reward
    u144      ;; Submission deadline (blocks)
    u288      ;; Evaluation deadline (blocks)
    u50       ;; Maximum submissions
)
```

### 2. Submitting a Solution

```clarity
(contract-call? .stacks-innovation-lab submit-innovative-solution
    u1  ;; Challenge ID
    u"Smart Carbon Tracker"
    u"An AI-powered system that tracks and optimizes carbon emissions in real-time"
    "a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890"  ;; Content hash
)
```
### 3. Authorizing Evaluators

```clarity
(contract-call? .stacks-innovation-lab authorize-expert-evaluator
    u1  ;; Challenge ID
    'SP1234...  ;; Evaluator principal
)
```
### 4. Evaluating Submissions

```clarity
(contract-call? .stacks-innovation-lab evaluate-solution-submission
    u1   ;; Submission ID
    u85  ;; Score (0-100)
    u"Excellent technical implementation with strong environmental impact potential"
)
```

### 5. Finalizing Challenge
```clarity
(contract-call? .stacks-innovation-lab finalize-challenge-with-winners
    u1  ;; Challenge ID
    (list u1 u3 u7)  ;; Winning submission IDs
)
```
### 6. Claiming Rewards

```clarity
(contract-call? .stacks-innovation-lab claim-winner-reward
    u1  ;; Challenge ID
)
```
##  API Reference
### Public Functions

#### Challenge Management
- **`establish-innovation-challenge`** - Create a new innovation challenge
- **`initiate-evaluation-phase`** - Transition challenge to evaluation phase
- **`finalize-challenge-with-winners`** - Finalize challenge and set winners

#### Participation
- **`submit-innovative-solution`** - Submit a solution to a challenge
- **`claim-winner-reward`** - Claim reward for winning submission

#### Evaluation
- **`authorize-expert-evaluator`** - Authorize an evaluator for a challenge
- **`evaluate-solution-submission`** - Evaluate a submitted solution

### Read-Only Functions

#### Data Queries
- **`get-challenge-details`** - Get challenge information
- **`get-submission-details`** - Get submission information
- **`get-evaluation-details`** - Get evaluation details
- **`verify-participant-submission-status`** - Check if participant submitted
- **`check-reward-claim-eligibility`** - Check reward claim status
- **`check-evaluator-authorization`** - Verify evaluator permissions
- **`get-platform-statistics`** - Get overall platform statistics

