##  Development Roadmap

### Phase 1 
- Core challenge lifecycle implementation
- Basic submission and evaluation system
- Reward distribution mechanism
- Security hardening

### Phase 2 
- Advanced evaluation mechanisms (weighted scoring)
- Challenge categories and tagging
- Enhanced reward distribution options
- Integration with external oracles

### Phase 3 
- DAO governance for platform decisions
- NFT certificates for winners
- Reputation system for evaluators
- Cross-chain challenge support